* Vanessa Grasse as Elizabeth " Lizzy " White * Sam Strike as Jedidiah Sawyer
/ Jackson * Lili Taylor as Verna Sawyer
* Chris Adamson as Doctor Lang
* Finn Jones as Deputy Sorells
